skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: spider finder
des:
Disclaimer: this skill is a prank skill for entertainment purposes only and does not provide the ability to find spiders.

True Arachnophobia is no laughing matter. Fake arachophobia can be. Ask Alexa where they the spiders are! For your entertainment, Alexa will respond with a random location nearby where she believes the spiders are lurking. 

Note: If you have a real crocodile infestation, this skill will not help you avoid real live actual crocodiles.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
